NYC Airbnb ML Pipeline
This project implements a complete ML pipeline using MLflow and modular components.
The pipeline downloads data, cleans it, validates it, splits it, and trains a Random Forest model.

Links Required for Udacity Review
🔗 Public W&B Project:  
https://wandb.ai/jknow46-western-governors-university/nyc_airbnb

