Outputs
After running the pipeline, you will have:

Code
data/clean_sample.csv
data/trainval.csv
data/test.csv
model.joblib
Notes
W&B runs in offline mode during the pipeline

Only numeric features are used for model training

Data validation tests must pass before training continues